 are non-sensitive opaque operational config already stored as identifiers; RDS SSE\n51\t  (storage-level) covers them`.\n52\t"}]},"uuid":"0e7576a1-da22-4506-a260-f782dcac3a28","timestamp":"2026-07-09T23:00:08.359Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"55b94416-bd3f-4603-bdd9-98073a4b3df9","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"C:\\Users\\brett\\OneDrive\\Documents\\GitHub\\meterly-pipeline-test","sessionId":"cb1e5971-0f87-4706-9a1d-09f830df9e6f","version":"2.1.205","gitBranch":"feature/quota-admin"}
